name: AI: Acrylic Intelligence #2
description:
The Acrylic Intelligence series consists entirely of AI-generated paintings, all created using a model trained exclusively with my physical acrylic paintings. I crave dynamic texture in my work and seek new ways of discovering fresh textures every day. I frequently subject my paintings to various forms of digital manipulation throughout my creation process, always chasing that next new "feeling". This time I decided to train a model using only physical paintings as inputs and see what the AI spits out. It did not disappoint.

Image #2 of a 11-still set; Series #1 of the AI: Acrylic Intelligence collection.
